  "body": "Syncing issue occurs on both iOS and Android.\r\nDoes not seem to be any consistency as to when syncing stalls, some report at 0%, some at 99% or anything in between.\r\n\r\nNeither relaunching nor reinstalling Status does not appear to fix issue.\r\n\r\nSome iOS users (https://instabug.com/applications/status/beta/bugs/80?status=New) reporting overheating issues during stall.\r\n\r\nSome users report the following message occurring after syncing stall\r\n\r\n```Error on param suggestions [{:command {:description \"Launch the browser\", :color \"#ffa500\", :name \"browse\", :params [{:name \"url\", :type \"text\", :value nil}], :type :command, :title \"Browser\", :has-handler false, :fullscreen true, :suggestions-trigger \"on-send\"}, :content \"c \", :chat-id \"wallet\"} {:error \"ReferenceError: 'call' is not defined\"}]```\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/25023739/21959934/be393cea-db3b-11e6-9240-5c0dcb48cea9.png)\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/25023739/21960030/16226514-db3f-11e6-8852-ba8ead76f84b.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nAndroid:\r\nhttps://instabug.com/applications/status-10bb8cbc-15f6-44f0-8c7a-db478dc34d7d/beta/bugs/189\r\nhttps://instabug.com/applications/status-10bb8cbc-15f6-44f0-8c7a-db478dc34d7d/beta/bugs/186\r\n\r\niOS:\r\nhttps://instabug.com/applications/status/beta/bugs/97?status=New\r\nhttps://instabug.com/applications/status/beta/bugs/94?status=New\r\nhttps://instabug.com/applications/status/beta/bugs/86?status=New\r\n\r\n",
