    "body": "Regarding syncing on iOS: it is very slow, it has never been fast. One of the reasons for this is that syncing doesn't work in background atm, so when a user opens another app or locks screen syncing stops. I don't see any other problems in reports related to iOS here, seems that `status-go` was functioning there.\r\n\r\nSo for iOS we need to figure how to make synchronization working in the background, at least I don't know how else we can improve this.",
